(35655, 107522, 0, 1, '賈斯特先生(Demo)', '', '2011-05-13 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 1, '　\r\nSomebody has a dream,but he never goes ahead\r\n　\r\nAll the reason that he says is”I just wanna play."\r\n\r\nPlay here, play there, and with all he can see\r\n\r\nThen everybody’s dream, he just destroyed\r\n\r\n\r\nDo you mind if you waste others’ time?\r\n\r\nEven dare not you carry the cross of  homicide?\r\n\r\n\r\n“Just”’s what people have, so I think that I met a Joker.\r\n\r\n“Just”’s what people have, but I don’t wanna be a Loser\r\n\r\nAs life goes on, someone just carry nothing.\r\n\r\nJust, and I know that having healthy legs is just a supreme disease.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSometimes in my eyes, the problem is not what you can’t\r\n\r\nBut the existence of your personality\r\n\r\nYou say “It’s just music, what the hell with you?”\r\n\r\nCuz  it’s just music, I got the fucking hell with me.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n“Just”’s what people have. You win everyone but you lose to yourself\r\n\r\n“Just”’s what people have. You win everyone but you lose to yourself\r\n\r\nAs life goes on, someone just carry nothing.\r\n\r\nJust, and I know that having healthy legs is just a supreme disease.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n有些人擁有一個夢想　但他卻從不努力前進\r\n\r\n所有他說的理由是　「我”只是”想要玩玩而已」\r\n\r\n左玩玩　右玩玩　伴隨著所有他能看見的東西\r\n\r\n接著每個人的夢想就這樣被他給破壞殆盡\r\n\r\n\r\n你可曾想過你是否一直在浪費別人的時間？\r\n\r\n還是甚至連這份殺人的罪你都不敢自己背？\r\n\r\n\r\n賈斯特　那即是人們的樣子　所以我想我遇到了一個小丑\r\n\r\n賈斯特　那即是人們的樣子　但是我可不想只當個失敗者\r\n\r\n當時間逐漸流逝　有些人卻始終一事無成\r\n\r\n賈斯特　我了解到　原來有雙健全的腿　才是最大的病態\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n有時在我看來　並不是你會什麼　不會什麼的問題\r\n\r\n而是你的「人格存在」根本有問題\r\n\r\n你說「這”只不過”是音樂而已　你發什麼神經？」\r\n\r\n但正因為是音樂　我他媽才要發神經\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n賈斯特　那即是人們的樣子　你贏了所有人卻輸給了你自己\r\n\r\n賈斯特　那即是人們的樣子　你贏了所有人卻輸給了你自己\r\n\r\n當時間逐漸流逝　有些人卻始終一事無成\r\n\r\n賈斯特　我了解到　原來有雙健全的腿　才是最大的病態\r\n　', '', 252, '', '黑色星期五', 'Black Friday', '黑の金曜日', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2011-05-13 13:00:43', '2015-03-12 13:47:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
